      {
        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Overview of Nanonets OCR S Image Text API"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "The Nanonets OCR S model (Nanonets_Ocr_S_F16) is optimized for extracting text from various image formats, supporting use cases like document digitization, invoice processing, and real-time data capture. It offers a RESTful API endpoint that accepts image inputs and returns structured text output, with support for multiple languages and complex layouts."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Setting Up API Integration"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "To integrate the Nanonets OCR S image text API, start by obtaining API credentials from the Nanonets dashboard. Use standard HTTP clients to send POST requests to the OCR endpoint. Ensure you handle authentication via API keys in headers and set appropriate content types for image uploads."
          }
        ]
      },
