        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Optimizing for Accuracy and Performance"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Pre-process images to enhance OCR results: resize to optimal dimensions (e.g., 1024x768), apply contrast adjustments, and remove noise. For batch processing, use asynchronous API calls to parallelize requests and reduce latency. Monitor response times and accuracy metrics via the API's built-in logging to fine-tune parameters like confidence thresholds."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
