            "type": "text",
            "text": "Scaling and Monitoring in Production"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Deploy the API integration behind a load balancer to distribute traffic across instances. Use cloud-based monitoring tools to track API usage, error rates, and throughput. Set up alerts for anomalies, and regularly review performance data to scale resources dynamically based on demand, ensuring consistent uptime and efficiency."
